Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:15.38,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我很担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}I'm very concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:17.67,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎非常担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}I'm very concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.80,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎如今 人们很容易忽略一个事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}It's easy today to lose sight of the fact
