Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:31.94,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎它们让失去联系的家人重聚 ‎找器官捐赠者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}They've reunited lost family members. They've found organ donors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:35.61,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎它们为整个世界带来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}I mean, there were meaningful, systemic changes happening
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:37.86,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎有意义的、系统的变革\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}around the world because of these platforms
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:40.20,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这是这些平台积极的一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}that were positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:44.53,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我认为我们对它的消极一面 ‎过度看轻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}I think we were naive about the flip side of that coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.58,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎对 这些东西 只要你发布 ‎它们自己就会存活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Yeah, these things, you release them, and they take on a life of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:52.00,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎它们被使用的方式 ‎与你当初的预期大相径庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And how they're used is pretty different than how you expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:56.50,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我深信 这些负面的后果 ‎不是任何人刻意为之\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Nobody, I deeply believe, ever intended any of these consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:59.55,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎没有任何一个坏人 没有 绝对没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}There's no one bad guy. No. Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.60,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎那么问题在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}So, then, what's the... what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎是否有问题？问题在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Is there a problem, and what is the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:20.15,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎是 很难给出一个单一的、简明的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Yeah, it is hard to give a single, succinct...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.11,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我在试着谈论很多不同的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}I'm trying to touch on many different problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:23.57,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎问题在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}What is the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:32.25,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎NETFLIX 原创纪录片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.34,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎虽然面对越来越多的质疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Despite facing mounting criticism,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.67,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这些所谓的大型技术公司却越发壮大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}the so-called Big Tech names are getting bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.92,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎整个技术产业 ‎正在面临全新维度的审查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}The entire tech industry is under a new level of scrutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.80,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎一项新的研究初步揭示了心理健康\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And a new study sheds light on the link
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.14,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎与社交媒体使用之间的联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}between mental health and social media use.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.47,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎来谈谈最新的研究…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Here to talk about the latest research...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:51.39,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎…的情况 根本没有保险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}...is going on that gets no coverage at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.10,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎数千万美国人无望地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Tens of millions of Americans are hopelessly addicted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.31,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎玩电子设备成瘾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}to their electronic devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.16,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎因为技术 现在你真的能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}It's exacerbated by the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:04:00.69,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,把自己‎隔离在一个泡泡内 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}that you can literally isolate yourself now
