Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.74,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,周围都是‎与你观点相似的人 ‎瘾性就更加恶化了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}in a bubble, thanks to our technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.57,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎虚假新闻变得更发达了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Fake news is becoming more advanced
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:06.78,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎威胁着全世界的社会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}and threatening societies around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:10.33,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我们12年多以前创造推特的时候 ‎根本没有想到这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}We weren't expecting any of this when we created Twitter over 12 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:12.50,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎官方说 他们没有理由相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}White House officials say they have no reason to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.75,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎俄罗斯网络攻击会停止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}the Russian cyberattacks will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:18.13,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎YouTube被迫专注于清理网站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}YouTube is being forced to concentrate on cleansing the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:21.55,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎如果你和十几岁的孩子去聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}TikTok, if you talk to any tween out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:24.01,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎他们是绝对不可能删除抖音的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}...there's no chance they'll delete this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:26.34,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎喂 艾拉 可以帮忙摆桌子吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Hey, Isla, can you get the table ready, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.51,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎有一个严肃的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}There's a question about whether social media
