Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.10,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎艾拉 可以帮忙摆桌子吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Isla, can you set the table, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.31,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎整容在青少年中已经十分受欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}These cosmetic procedures are becoming so popular with teens,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.90,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎整容医生甚至造出了一种新病征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}plastic surgeons have coined a new syndrome for it,
