Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:43.74,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎让自己看上去 ‎更接近加了滤镜的自拍中的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}so they can look more like they do in filtered selfies.
