Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:14.68,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎它们付钱 交换给你展示广告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}They pay in exchange for showing their ads to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:18.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我们是产品 我们的关注 ‎就是卖给广告商的产品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}We're the product. Our attention is the product being sold to advertisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:20.44,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这样说 过于简单化了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}That's a little too simplistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:23.65,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎产品其实是我们行为和认知的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}It's the gradual, slight, imperceptible change
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:26.28,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎逐渐的、一点一点的 ‎我们未察觉到的变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}in your own behavior and perception that is the product.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.57,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‎（行为和认知的 变化）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.24,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这才是产品 是唯一可能的产品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And that is the product. It's the only possible product.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:34.08,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这其中 没有任何东西 ‎能再被称为产品了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}There's nothing else on the table that could possibly be called the product.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:37.25,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这是他们能拿来赚钱的唯一东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}That's the only thing there is for them to make money from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.25,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎改变你做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Changing what you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.71,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎你的思维模式 改变你这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}how you think, who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.30,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这是一种逐渐的变化 非常轻微\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}It's a gradual change. It's slight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:48.97,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎如果你去找一个人 ‎你说：“给我一千万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}If you can go to somebody and you say, "Give me $10 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:54.31,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我会让世界往你希望的方向改变1%…”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}and I will change the world one percent in the direction you want it to change..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:58.18,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎是整个世界！这就很神奇 值很多钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}It's the world! That can be incredible, and that's worth a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.14,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:04.57,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这是每种商业都一直梦想的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}This is what every business has always dreamt of:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:10.91,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎就是投放一个广告 ‎有一定能够成功的保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}to have a guarantee that if it places an ad, it will be successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.99,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这就是他们的生意 ‎他们卖的是确定性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}That's their business. They sell certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:14.91,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‎（确定性）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.62,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎为了在这个生意中成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}In order to be successful in that business,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:19.58,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎你必须要有优秀的预判能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}you have to have great predictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:20.54,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‎（优秀的预判能力）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:24.17,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎优秀的预判能力始于一个必要条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Great predictions begin with one imperative:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.92,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎你需要很多数据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}you need a lot of data.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.05,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‎（数据）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:31.55,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎很多人把它称作监视资本主义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Many people call this surveillance capitalism,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:34.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎资本主义利用大型技术公司 ‎对每个人去的每一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}capitalism profiting off of the infinite tracking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:38.06,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎进行无限追踪获利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}of everywhere everyone goes by large technology companies
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎大型技术公司的商业模式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}whose business model is to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.85,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎是保证广告商能尽最大可能成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}that advertisers are as successful as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.56,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这是现在的一种新市场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}This is a new kind of marketplace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.07,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这种市场 以前从未出现过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}It's a marketplace that never existed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:55.37,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这个市场交易的 只有人类期货\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And it's a marketplace that trades exclusively in human futures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:16:01.58,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎就像交易五花肉期货 ‎和石油期货的市场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Just like there are markets that trade in pork belly futures or oil futures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:07.59,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我们现在有了 ‎交易大范围人类期货的市场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}We now have markets that trade in human futures at scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:13.47,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这些市场创造了万亿美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}and those markets have produced the trillions of dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:19.26,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎让网络公司成为了人类历史上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}that have made the Internet companies the richest companies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:22.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎最富有的公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}in the history of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:31.07,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我想让人们知道的是 ‎他们在网上做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}What I want people to know is that everything they're doing online
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:34.32,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎都被监控着 被追踪着 被评估着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}is being watched, is being tracked, is being measured.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:39.62,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎你所做出的每一个行为 ‎都被小心翼翼地监控着、记录着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Every single action you take is carefully monitored and recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:43.83,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎具体到你停在哪一张图片上看了 ‎你看了多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Exactly what image you stop and look at, for how long you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.79,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎是的 真的 看了多久都记录了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC} yeah, seriously, for how long you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.54,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‎（纳维亚 参与时间）\N\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.34,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‎（瑞恩 参与时间）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.42,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‎（雷恩 参与时间）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.10,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎人们孤独的时候 他们知道 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}They know when people are lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.80,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎人们抑郁的时候 他们知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}They know when people are depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:57.09,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎人们看前任爱侣的时候 他们知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}They know when people are looking at photos of your ex-romantic partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:00.85,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎你深夜在做什么 他们知道 ‎他们全都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}They know what you're doing late at night. They know the entire thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.23,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎你是内向还是外向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Whether you're an introvert or an extrovert,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:06.81,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎你的神经哪种类型 ‎你的性格是哪种类型\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}or what kind of neuroses you have, what your personality type is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:11.61,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎他们所掌握的我们的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}They have more information about us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:14.32,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎超越人类历史上所有的想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}than has ever been imagined in human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.36,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这是史无前例的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}It is unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:22.79,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎所有这些我们不经意间 ‎不断流露出的数据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And so, all of this data that we're... that we're just pouring out all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:26.75,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎都被输入到这些系统中 ‎几乎不用人类看管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}is being fed into these systems that have almost no human supervision
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:30.88,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎会做出越来越好的预判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}and that are making better and better and better and better predictions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.55,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎预判出我们要做什么 ‎我们是怎样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}about what we're gonna do and... and who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.34,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‎（为您推荐）\N\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:39.55,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎很多人有一种误解 认为被卖掉的 ‎是我们的数据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}People have the misconception it's our data being sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:43.18,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎脸书的商业兴趣 ‎肯定不是放掉这些数据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}It's not in Facebook's business interest to give up the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.10,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎他们用这些数据做什么呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}What do they do with that data?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:54.49,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎他们做出预判我们行为的模型\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}They build models that predict our actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.61,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎拥有最优秀模型的公司就赢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}and whoever has the best model wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.04,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎他向下滑网页的速度慢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}His scrolling speed is slowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:05.97,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎接近他平均阅读一屏时间长度的末尾 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Nearing the end of his average session length.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.08,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎减少广告加载\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Decreasing ad load.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:08.33,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎把朋友和家人弄回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Pull back on friends and family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.34,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎在屏幕的另一端\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}On the other side of the screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:15.46,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎他们就好像拥有一个 ‎我们的巫毒娃娃化身一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}it's almost as if they had this avatar voodoo doll-like model of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.18,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我们做过的所有事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}All of the things we've ever done,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:19.47,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎点击过的每一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}all the clicks we've ever made,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.64,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我们看过的所有视频 ‎点赞过的所有内容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}all the videos we've watched, all the likes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:25.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这些数据都会被返回去 ‎用来建造一个越来越精准的模型\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}that all gets brought back into building a more and more accurate model.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.48,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎一旦有了这个模型\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}The model, once you have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.85,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎就能预判这个人做怎样的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}you can predict the kinds of things that person does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:31.77,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎好 让我测试一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Right, let me just test.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:33.48,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎你将要去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Where you'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:36.11,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我能预判出 ‎你会继续看什么样的视频\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}I can predict what kind of videos will keep you watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:39.15,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我能预判 ‎什么样的情感更能让你产生共鸣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}I can predict what kinds of emotions tend to trigger you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.41,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎好 完美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Yes, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:42.78,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎年度最悲壮失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}The most epic fails of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:44.66,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‎（悲壮失败）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:51.08,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎-完美 有效果 ‎-接着另一个视频\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}-Perfect. That worked. -Following with another video.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.04,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎漂亮 在它开始之前 ‎我们插进去一个运动鞋广告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Beautiful. Let's squeeze in a sneaker ad before it starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.72,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎很多这种技术公司有三个主要目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}At a lot of technology companies, there's three main goals.
