Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.96,0:39:10.34,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎不需要每隔五分钟 ‎就获得一次社交认可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}to have social approval being dosed to us every five minutes.
