Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.61,0:39:25.15,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎给我们奖赏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}hearts, likes, thumbs-up
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.23,0:39:28.40,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我们把它融合到价值中 ‎融合到真相中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}and we conflate that with value, and we conflate it with truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.82,0:39:33.12,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎不论是否虚假 易破碎的人气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And instead, what it really is is fake, brittle popularity...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.91,0:39:37.45,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这是短期的 你需要承认 这让你更加\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}that's short-term and that leaves you even more, and admit it,
