Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.26,0:39:50.84,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎想一下 这种现象被20亿人复杂化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Think about that compounded by two billion people,
