Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.16,0:40:57.66,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎现在增长了151%\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}they are up 151 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.83,0:41:01.70,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这个增长模式 指向了社交媒体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And that pattern points to social media.
