Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.31,0:41:29.19,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎整个一代人都更加焦虑 ‎更加脆弱、更加抑郁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}A whole generation is more anxious, more fragile, more depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.61,0:41:33.28,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎他们更不愿意冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}They're much less comfortable taking risks.
