Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.50,0:41:49.71,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎整个一代人 有了真正的改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}This is a real change in a generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.17,0:41:57.30,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎别忘了 这些人中的每一个 ‎每一个住院的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And remember, for every one of these, for every hospital admission,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.38,0:42:00.26,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎背后都有一个受伤的、惊恐的家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}there's a family that is traumatized and horrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.35,0:42:02.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎“天啊 我的孩子们怎么了？”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}"My God, what is happening to our kids?"
