Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.87,0:42:28.12,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这些服务正在杀人 ‎也在导致人们自杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}These services are killing people... and causing people to kill themselves.
