Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.80,0:42:42.56,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎让他们将自己 ‎和不切实际的审美标准相对比”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}making them compare themselves to unrealistic standards of beauty."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.64,0:42:44.68,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎没有人希望那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Like, no one wants that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.10,0:42:46.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎没有一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}No one does.
