Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.81,0:44:56.69,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎但这个说法没有注意到的是 ‎有些东西明显是全新的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And what this misses is there's something distinctly new here.
