Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.99,0:45:09.08,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎大体上 ‎如果你看从20世纪60年代至今\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Roughly, if you say from, like, the 1960s to today,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.87,0:45:12.96,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎计算机处理能力增长了万亿倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}processing power has gone up about a trillion times.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.79,0:45:18.34,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我们身边没有任何其他东西 ‎以这个速率增长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Nothing else that we have has improved at anything near that rate.
