Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.26,0:45:25.26,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎几乎所有其他的东西都显得微不足道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And almost everything else is negligible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.34,0:45:27.18,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎或许最重要的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And perhaps most importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.26,0:45:31.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我们人类… 我们的生理 ‎我们的大脑 根本没有丝毫进化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}our humanour physiology, our brains have evolved not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.85,0:45:35.23,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‎（没有手机的时间）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}
