Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.30,0:46:10.55,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎然后出现了这样一个屏幕 ‎在屏幕的另一端\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}and then there's this screen, and then on the opposite side of the screen,
