Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.64,0:46:16.10,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎有着与你不同的目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}that have goals that are different than your goals,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.19,0:46:19.69,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎那么 这个游戏谁能赢呢？谁会赢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}and so, who's gonna win in that game? Who's gonna win?
