Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.16,0:46:34.08,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎-或许吧 ‎-或许是广告太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}-Probably. -Well, maybe it was all the ads.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.16,0:46:37.79,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎不 一定出了严重的问题 ‎我们切换到复苏模式吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}No. Something's very wrong. Let's switch to resurrection mode.
