Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.63,0:46:48.68,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我会回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.76,0:46:51.01,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎…你会看到无人机 你觉得 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}You see drones, and you think, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.01,0:46:52.68,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎“人工智能会杀人的”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}" we're gonna kill people with AI."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.64,0:46:59.81,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎人们忽略的是 人工智能 ‎现在已经在运营着当今世界了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And what people miss is that AI already runs today's world right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.90,0:47:03.23,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎甚至谈论“人工智能”都只是暗喻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Even talking about "an AI" is just a metaphor.
