Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.32,0:47:13.12,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎有些在地下 有些在水下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}some of them underground, some of them underwater,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.20,0:47:14.49,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎房间里全是电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}of just computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.58,0:47:17.83,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎无数的电脑 连绵不绝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Tons and tons of computers, as far as the eye can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.46,0:47:20.50,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎它们互相之间在内部深度连接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}They're deeply interconnected with each other
