Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.00,0:47:26.00,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎始终不停地在彼此之间交换信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}sending information back and forth between each other all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.80,0:47:28.59,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎他们会运行很多不同的程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}And they'll be running many different programs,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.67,0:47:30.80,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎在同样的机器上 有不同的产品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}many different products on those same machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.34,0:47:33.68,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎有些东西可以被描述为简单算法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Some of those things could be described as simple algorithms,
