Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.36,0:47:51.57,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎算法被某种成功的定义优化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}Algorithms are optimized to some definition of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.24,0:47:53.37,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎所以 如果你能想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}So, if you can imagine,
