Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.20,0:47:59.29,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎需要依靠算法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}to their definition of success,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.83,0:48:01.21,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎那就是商业利益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\1c&H003CA8DC}it's a coercial interest.
